      • collectInformation

        public final void collectInformation(ProgressIndicator progress)
        Description copied from interface: HighlightingPass
        Asks this pass to start analysis and hold collected information. This method is called from a background thread.
        Specified by:
        collectInformation in interface HighlightingPass
        Parameters:
        progress - to check if highlighting process is cancelled. Pass is to check progress.isCanceled() as often as possible and throw ProcessCanceledException if true is returned. See also ProgressIndicator.checkCanceled().
